('74296','25740','5','Exceptional luxury frontline penthouse in Sol de Mallorca'),
('74297','25741','5','Sol de Mallorca belongs to the municipality of Calvia and is located in the south west of Mallorca. This exclusive complex of luxury apartments is situated directly at the coast and offers stunning sea views.\r\nThe penthouse is located on the 3rd floor and is easily accessible from the garage by elevator. The living space of approx. 280 m² composes of a very spacious living room, 4 bedrooms, 4 elegant bathrooms (2 en suite), a modern fitted kitchen, a laundry room, an office room and pantry. Large double-glazed sliding windows made of teak provide stunning views over the spacious terrace and out to sea. Air conditioning h / c and gas central heating create a comfortable room climate all year round. The underground garage offers 1-2 parking spaces. The complex boasts a beautiful pool area with sun terraces. The furniture could be purchased as well (price negotiable).\r\nThis luxury penthouse apartment is also for rent, minimum renting period is 1 year. The monthly rent will be 5.000,- €, 12 months’ rent have to be paid in advance plus 3 months’ rent as deposit. The commission fee is 1.5 months rent plus VAT and will be paid by the tenant.'),
